1
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:43,680
What are you doing?

2
00:01:44,359 --> 00:01:45,599
There's something wrong with these herbs.

3
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:54,719
I saw him injecting something into them.

4
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,760
Chief Pharmacist Lu.

5
00:02:05,719 --> 00:02:06,439
Go on ahead, you two.

6
00:02:06,439 --> 00:02:07,000
Okay.

7
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:07,840
We'll head back then.

8
00:02:23,599 --> 00:02:24,960
Lu Tanxiang, what nonsense is this?

9
00:02:42,759 --> 00:02:44,560
I see nothing wrong with these herbs.

10
00:02:46,639 --> 00:02:47,560
Yunfan, you have to believe me.

11
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:48,719
I'm not lying.

12
00:02:48,719 --> 00:02:50,199
Something really was injected into them.

13
00:02:50,199 --> 00:02:51,280
I saw it with my own eyes.

14
00:02:53,039 --> 00:02:53,680
Lu Tanxiang.

15
00:02:54,599 --> 00:02:56,520
I've already cut all ties with you.

16
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:58,000
You stay the pampered princess,

17
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:59,080
and I'll stay a son of the Yang family.

18
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:00,120
We owe each other nothing.

19
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:01,479
And we leave each other alone.

20
00:03:01,479 --> 00:03:02,719
Showing up now to disrupt my match,

21
00:03:02,719 --> 00:03:03,599
what's that supposed to mean?

22
00:03:03,599 --> 00:03:04,479
I didn't.

23
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:08,120
Young Yang, care to inspect them?

24
00:03:10,039 --> 00:03:10,520
That won't be necessary.

25
00:03:42,879 --> 00:03:44,319
Why is he coughing up blood?

26
00:03:44,319 --> 00:03:46,360
Could the herbs really be tainted?

27
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:48,120
Didn't he just say the herbs were fine?

28
00:03:49,599 --> 00:03:51,199
Yang Yunfan must've prescribed wrong.

29
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:57,360
Looks like your prescription failed.

30
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:58,840
Why?

31
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,719
How is this possible?

32
00:04:00,719 --> 00:04:02,080
My prescription is completely fine!

33
00:04:02,919 --> 00:04:05,719
No!

34
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:11,159
Why is this happening?

35
00:04:11,159 --> 00:04:12,680
You're really overacting.

36
00:04:18,759 --> 00:04:19,680
I thought it was pretty natural.

37
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:27,560
Here.

38
00:04:35,399 --> 00:04:36,560
Everyone, please look over here.

39
00:04:50,639 --> 00:04:53,279
Which box did Uncle Ye put it in?

40
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,560
Qingxue.

41
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:18,639
I made this from a rare crystal I found.

42
00:05:18,639 --> 00:05:21,360
It reveals the true form of Vile Qi.

43
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:23,639
Even ordinary people can see it.

44
00:05:23,639 --> 00:05:26,399
But it only works at a specific hour.

45
00:05:26,399 --> 00:05:29,160
When Purple Qi peaks in heaven and earth.

46
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:31,360
Only then can it briefly activate.

47
00:05:34,439 --> 00:05:35,720
Purple Qi,

48
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:38,360
the primordial breath of creation.

49
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:40,560
Practitioners use the body as a cauldron,

50
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:42,600
refining the essence of sun and moon,

51
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:44,519
and the qi of mountains and plants,

52
00:05:44,519 --> 00:05:46,319
transforming it into Purple Qi.

53
00:05:46,319 --> 00:05:47,720
It can banish all evils,

54
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:51,399
open meridians, purge toxins,
glimpse life and death,

55
00:05:51,399 --> 00:05:53,439
and reveal the essence of medicine.

56
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:02,439
Excellent.

57
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:03,959
This time,

58
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:06,600
we can catch them all in one sweep.

59
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:10,360
Since my mother was infected with Vile Qi,

60
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:13,240
my father devoted years to researching it,

61
00:06:13,959 --> 00:06:16,319
until he himself got infected too.

62
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:19,759
This crystal was his life's work.

63
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:23,199
The Glazed Evil-Detecting Crystal.

64
00:06:23,199 --> 00:06:26,519
It makes invisible Vile Qi visible to all.

65
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,120
Vile Qi?

66
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,480
What the heck is that?

67
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,680
Have you ever heard of it?

68
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,759
Nope.

69
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,879
There's Vile Qi on these herbs too.

70
00:06:49,199 --> 00:06:50,560
Looks like the herbs really are tainted.

71
00:06:51,639 --> 00:06:53,000
Someone's sabotaging us in the shadows.

72
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,920
If I remember correctly,

73
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,439
these herbs

74
00:07:04,439 --> 00:07:06,639
were handed to me by Chief Pharmacist Lu.

75
00:07:08,839 --> 00:07:10,959
Young Master Yang, what are you implying?

76
00:07:11,639 --> 00:07:12,480
Xiangyang.

77
00:07:13,879 --> 00:07:14,560
Come here.

78
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:18,079
Stop playing dumb.

79
00:07:18,079 --> 00:07:20,560
Your own daughter just identified you.

80
00:07:22,319 --> 00:07:24,839
So everything Miss Lu said was true.

81
00:07:24,839 --> 00:07:26,680
Truly putting justice above family.

82
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:27,920
Indeed.

83
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,160
Utter nonsense!

84
00:07:34,759 --> 00:07:37,199
You should recognize this transport log.

85
00:07:44,759 --> 00:07:47,759
This log details the past three months

86
00:07:47,759 --> 00:07:51,079
of every herb transfer between
Green Wood and Mystic Water Halls.

87
00:07:51,079 --> 00:07:54,199
Including this batch of tainted herbs,

88
00:07:54,199 --> 00:07:56,759
handled by Mystic Water Hall's Lu Ning,

89
00:07:56,759 --> 00:07:58,040
delivered to the Misty Herb Sanctuary.

90
00:08:05,199 --> 00:08:06,399
This transport log alone...

91
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:10,199
What does this log prove?

92
00:08:10,199 --> 00:08:11,399
At most, it only proves

93
00:08:11,399 --> 00:08:13,560
that Mystic Water Hall handled transport.

94
00:08:14,519 --> 00:08:16,959
As for the tainted herbs you mentioned,

95
00:08:16,959 --> 00:08:18,000
you claim I swapped them?

96
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:20,120
How dare you frame me without proof?

97
00:08:21,639 --> 00:08:22,480
Besides,

98
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:25,480
Mystic Water Hall's herb transport

99
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:27,639
has always been meticulous.

100
00:08:27,639 --> 00:08:31,360
And this so-called Lu Ning you mentioned,

101
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,279
sorry to disappoint,

102
00:08:32,279 --> 00:08:35,159
Mystic Water Hall has no such person.

103
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,159
Chief Pharmacist Lu,

104
00:08:41,039 --> 00:08:43,200
you won't give up until you hit a wall.

105
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:49,919
Father actually gathered this many

106
00:08:49,919 --> 00:08:51,480
transport logs from Mystic Water Hall.

107
00:08:52,799 --> 00:08:53,320
Look,

108
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:55,399
every entry is recorded in detail.

109
00:08:56,639 --> 00:08:57,720
Uncle Ye was well prepared.

110
00:08:58,919 --> 00:09:00,960
He'd long anticipated that these people

111
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:02,000
would scheme behind the scenes.

112
00:09:04,480 --> 00:09:06,000
What's more,

113
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:06,960
every single page

114
00:09:07,639 --> 00:09:09,000
bears the name Lu Ning.

115
00:09:09,559 --> 00:09:12,639
Who exactly is this Lu Ning?

116
00:09:13,879 --> 00:09:14,879
As I recall,

117
00:09:15,799 --> 00:09:17,200
he's Lu Daozai's right-hand man.

118
00:09:18,159 --> 00:09:20,360
He used to handle external transport.

119
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:23,080
Perfect.

120
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:25,200
Then let's follow this thread

121
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,399
and dig up all their secrets.

122
00:09:30,159 --> 00:09:30,679
What do you say?

123
00:09:30,679 --> 00:09:33,679
I've checked the herb logs three times.

124
00:09:33,679 --> 00:09:34,720
On the surface, there's no flaw.

125
00:09:35,159 --> 00:09:36,960
The signatures are airtight.

126
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:39,440
Even the intake procedures were flawless.

127
00:09:46,639 --> 00:09:48,600
If nothing went wrong at the signing,

128
00:09:49,759 --> 00:09:50,600
then the problem must lie

129
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,159
in transit before the herbs were stored.

130
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:54,960
In other words,

131
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:56,440
before entering the storehouse,

132
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,480
these herbs were already tampered with.

133
00:09:58,919 --> 00:10:01,639
But I sent someone to look into Lu Ning,

134
00:10:01,639 --> 00:10:02,679
and couldn't find a single trace.

135
00:10:05,759 --> 00:10:06,679
I have a way.

136
00:10:24,559 --> 00:10:25,240
There.

137
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,320
The residual Gu poison in your body

138
00:10:27,879 --> 00:10:29,000
has been completely cleared out.

139
00:10:30,159 --> 00:10:31,759
Just remember to take your meds on time.

140
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:40,799
Now,

141
00:10:40,799 --> 00:10:41,320
you're free.

142
00:10:42,759 --> 00:10:43,440
Thank you.

143
00:10:47,399 --> 00:10:48,159
Wait, my lady.

144
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:57,759
There's still one thing

145
00:10:58,519 --> 00:10:59,720
you promised me that you haven't done.

146
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:06,639
Stop calling me "my lady."

147
00:11:07,879 --> 00:11:08,840
I do have a name.

148
00:11:10,559 --> 00:11:11,159
Ghost Blade.

149
00:11:12,639 --> 00:11:15,720
That doesn't sound like a real name.

150
00:11:16,919 --> 00:11:18,600
If you hadn't mentioned it,

151
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:20,720
I'd have nearly forgotten my real name.

152
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:25,000
It really doesn't matter.

153
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:26,240
A name, you know,

154
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:26,960
is just a symbol.

155
00:11:30,879 --> 00:11:33,000
Because everyone who knew my real name

156
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,080
is gone now.

157
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:35,639
Then you don't have to tell me.

158
00:11:36,879 --> 00:11:37,399
Lin Hongxiu.

159
00:11:40,519 --> 00:11:41,759
My name is Lin Hongxiu.

160
00:11:43,159 --> 00:11:45,639
That's a really lovely name.

161
00:11:48,759 --> 00:11:49,720
So,

162
00:11:50,759 --> 00:11:53,039
does this make us

163
00:11:53,039 --> 00:11:54,279
partners who share a secret?

164
00:11:55,679 --> 00:11:56,320
Go on.

165
00:11:56,919 --> 00:11:57,759
What do you want me to do?

166
00:11:59,080 --> 00:11:59,720
Even if it's

167
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:02,120
giving myself to you.

168
00:12:12,159 --> 00:12:13,799
Stop teasing me already.

169
00:12:17,720 --> 00:12:19,720
You really can't take a joke.

170
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:22,399
Go on, what is it?

171
00:12:26,879 --> 00:12:28,799
There's someone in Mystic Water Hall

172
00:12:28,799 --> 00:12:29,799
named Lu Ning.

173
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:33,000
I need you to investigate him secretly.

174
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,240
Find out everything about him.

175
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:36,159
See who he usually associates with.

176
00:12:36,159 --> 00:12:37,200
But you must be careful.

177
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:38,000
Don't let word get out.

178
00:12:38,519 --> 00:12:39,519
See what clues you can find.

179
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:47,000
Are you questioning my expertise?

180
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:48,279
Don't worry.

181
00:12:48,279 --> 00:12:49,639
I know what to do.

182
00:12:52,279 --> 00:12:53,399
I got so nervous

183
00:12:53,399 --> 00:12:55,320
I forgot this is your specialty.

184
00:12:59,159 --> 00:13:01,600
I love seeing you all flustered like this.

185
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:05,039
Wait for my news.

186
00:13:12,159 --> 00:13:13,399
Be careful, okay?

187
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:16,679
There's no way they'll catch me.

188
00:13:18,080 --> 00:13:18,840
You

189
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:24,639
really don't play by the rules.
